module.exports = "🌯 Welcome to Kebab House\n\nWelcome to Kebab House – where authentic flavor meets a passion for quality street food. We serve freshly prepared kebabs, juicy grilled meat, crisp vegetables, and homemade sauces you’ll fall in love with from the very first bite.\n\n🔥 Flavor That Brings You Back\n\nEvery day, we grill high-quality meat and wrap it in fresh bread or soft tortillas. Whether you’re craving a classic döner, a loaded box, or a full plate, there’s always something for you to enjoy.\n\n🥗 Freshness Comes First\n\nWe use only fresh ingredients – vegetables are prepared daily, sauces are made in-house using our own recipes, and every meal is crafted with care and attention to detail.\n\n🚀 Fast, Tasty, Honest\n\nWhether you’re on the go or taking your time, Kebab House is here for you. Quick service, great atmosphere, and food you’ll want to come back for.\n\n📍 Visit Us Today\n\nCome and taste real kebab – we’re looking forward to seeing you!";

